room_title: Escape room "The Titanic and the Curse of the Mummy" by Escape History in Warren
review: We failed to break the curse on the Titanic but had a great time!!! Loved the set up of the room and the challenging clues!!! We will definitely be back to try the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "The Titanic and the Curse of the Mummy" by Escape History in Warren
review: Such a fun time! The decor really fits the era. We did the Titanic room and though we were just short of getting out, we had an awesome time. Highly recommend!
